IF you can find a Mexican clamp, you'll find it matches our German  
hardware. The Brazil front beam isn't the same as the German one.

I know of no vendors selling the Mexican VW clamp. I was able to  
track down a clamp through the VW dealers but I didn't always have  
good luck:

